          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1671537084088-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and <strong>chopped potato </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the onion has softened</p><p>Add a pinch of your <strong>berbere seasoning</strong> and the <strong>softened butter</strong> to a bowl and mix it all together, then set aside – this is your <strong>berbere-spiced butter</strong></p>",
