          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1671537105352-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1671537105352-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1671537105352-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the potato is nearly fork-tender, add your <strong>naan[s]</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once done, remove the <strong>warmed naan[s]</strong> from the<strong> toaster </strong>and spread with the <strong>berbere-spiced butter </strong>– this is your<strong> berbere-spiced butter naan[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Mini-naans-in-toaster-1704990781602-x200.jpg",
